      implementation="Implemented a rough Bergomi model utilizing a hybrid scheme combining exact simulation of the variance process and Euler stepping. Calibration performed via a machine learning accelerated Levenberg–Marquardt algorithm."
      outcome="Demonstrated a 40% reduction in out-of-sample pricing errors for options with expiries under one month. The Hurst parameter stabilized near 0.12 across major equity indices."
      stack={[
